1686
01:59:50,642 --> 01:59:51,943
Well...

1687
01:59:52,878 --> 01:59:54,746
shit.

1688
01:59:59,618 --> 02:00:01,519
<i>Commander, I have an idea.</i>

1689
02:00:01,520 --> 02:00:03,253
