air as a thruster...

1693
02:00:11,963 --> 02:00:13,696
<i>and fly towards you.</i>

1694
02:00:13,697 --> 02:00:17,167
<i>It would be easy to control
because it would be on my arm.</i>

1695
02:00:17,168 --> 02:00:19,003
